OL,3,C'World's highest electricity price'
OL,4,Cslashed in half after backlash
OL,6,FThe cost of electricity in Sark will
OL,7,Fbe slashed by more than half as the
OL,8,Fisland's regulator brings in price
OL,9,Fcontrols to reverse recent rises.
OL,11,FFrom 1 October, customers can only be
OL,12,Fcharged a maximum of 52p per unit - it
OL,13,Fhad spiralled to #1.14 in September.
OL,15,FSark Electricity Limited (SEL) had
OL,16,Fjustified the increase by saying it is
OL,17,Fpartly needed to cover ongoing legal
OL,18,Fcosts to fight an attempted compulsory
OL,19,Fpurchase by the island's government
OL,20,FChief Pleas, but the Price Control
OL,21,FCommissioner, Shane Lynch, disagreed.
