OL,3,C'World's highest electricity price'
OL,4,Cslashed in half after backlash
OL,6,FHe ruled that the recent changes to
OL,7,Fcharges, which amounted to a 132%
OL,8,Frise, are "neither fair nor
OL,9,Freasonable" and said "by a long shot,
OL,10,Fthe highest price in the world for
OL,11,Felectricity".
OL,13,FAlongside the much lower maximum unit
OL,14,Fcost for customers, there is also a
OL,15,Freduction in meter charges.
OL,17,FThe price for single-phase meters will
OL,18,Fdrop from #10 to a limit of #3.43 per
OL,19,Fmonth, while three-phase meters stand
OL,20,Fat #4.65.
