OL,6,FA maximum monthly standby charge for
OL,7,F'own-generators' has been set at #5
OL,8,Fper kilowatt-hour.
OL,10,FEffectively, the Commissioner says,
OL,11,Fthese changes together will see
OL,12,Fconsumers paying the same amount for
OL,13,Felectricity as they were back in
OL,14,FAugust.
OL,16,FThe limits will last for two years but
OL,17,Fcan be adjusted for changes such as
OL,18,Fvariations in inflation and fuel costs.
