OL,6,FThe order is not retrospective, so it
OL,7,Fwill not cover September's higher
OL,8,Ftariffs.
OL,10,FCustomers who are concerned about
OL,11,Fpaying this bill are asked to contact
OL,12,FSEL directly, while vulnerable
OL,13,Fresidents can reach out to the Island
OL,14,FSafeguarding Officer or the Sark
OL,15,FMedical and Emergency Services
OL,16,FCommittee for support.
